\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Please bore someone else with your questions.\'a0And make sure we have Pier 59 at 8:00 a.m. tomorrow.\'a0Remind Jocelyn I need to see a few of those satchels that Marc is doing in the pony. And then tell Simone I'll take Jackie if Maggie isn't available.\'a0Did Demarchelier confirm?\'a0\
