\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And, Emily?\'a0That's all.\'a0\uc0\u8232 It's just the cavalier disregard for clear directions...Do you have Demarchelier?\
