\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 No. And I've seen all this before.\'a0Where are all the other dresses?\'a0No. No, I just...It's just baffling to me.\'a0\uc0\u8232 Why is it so impossible to put together a decent run-through?\'a0You people have had hours and hours to prepare. It's just so confusing to me. Where are the advertisers?\'a0\
