\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 My flight has been canceled.\'a0It's some absurd weather problem.\'a0I need to get home tonight. The twins have a recital tomorrow morning at school.\'a0At school!\'a0Good.\'a0\
