\ls3\ilvl0\cf3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Please. It's just...I don't know...drizzling.\'a0Someone must be getting out.\'a0Call Donatella. Get her jet.\'a0Call everybody else that we know that has a jet. Irv?\'a0Call every...This is your responsibi...This is your job.\'a0Get me home.\cf2 \strokec2 \
