\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The girls' recital was absolutely wonderful.\'a0They played Rachmaninoff. Everyone loved it.\'a0Everyone except me\'a0because, sadly, I was not there.\'a0\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf3 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Do you know why I hired you?\'a0I always hire the same girl -\'a0stylish, slender, of course,\'a0worships the magazine.\'a0But so often, they turn out to be,\'a0I don't know,\'a0disappointing and stupid.\'a0So you, with that impressive resume\'a0and the big speech about your so-called work ethic,\'a0I thought you would be different.\'a0I said to myself, go ahead.\'a0Hire the smart, fat girl.\'a0I had hope.\'a0My God. I live on it.\'a0Anyway, you ended up disappointing me more than\'a0more than any of the other silly girls.\'a0That's all.\'a0\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
